%section#wv-givehope.white
  .shadow
  .container
    .row
      .col-xs-12
        %h1
          give hope this christmas
          %img{:src => '/images/advent/icn-love-all.png', :style => 'width: 100px; height: 100px'}
    .row
      .col-xs-12
        %p
          At Winchester Vineyard Church we provide opportunities for people to help others in our community and abroad. Here are a few ways you can give someone hope this Christmas.
        %p
          Please bring all donations between 10am and 3pm Monday, Tuesday or Thursday to
          %a{:href => 'https://www.google.co.uk/maps/place/Winchester+Vineyard/@51.0528351,-1.3089904,17z/data=!3m1!4b1!4m5!3m4!1s0x48741279301ad1dd:0xbf5c56d3959f4861!8m2!3d51.0528351!4d-1.3068017'} Winchester Vineyard Church, Bar End Industrial Estate, Bar End Rd, Winchester SO23 9NP.
          Or bring donations on Sunday to one of our services at 10:30am or 6:30pm.
    .row
      .col-md-6
        %h2 pack a shoebox
        %img{:src => '/images/givehope/shoeboxes.jpg'}
        %p
          These will be sent to children abroad who will otherwise receive no Christmas gifts.
          %a{:href => 'https://www.samaritans-purse.org.uk/what-we-do/operation-christmas-child/how-to-pack-a-shoebox/'} Click here for instructions
          and fill your shoe box (ready made boxes available at the Vineyard for 50p) &amp; return to the Vineyard
          %strong by 12 November.
      .col-md-6
        %h2 donate to our toy fair
        %img{:src => '/images/givehope/toyfair.jpg'}
        %p
          We give away toys, books, games and stocking fillers for families in Winchester who can’t afford much for their children at Christmas. Please bring us new toys to donate for children aged 0-16
          %strong by 3 December.
    .row
      .col-md-6
        %h2 give a hamper
        %img{:src => '/images/givehope/hamper.jpg'}
        %p
          Food hampers to make Christmas special for families in Winchester – please take a foodstore bag from our foyer with the short shopping list attached, fill the bag &amp; return it.
        %p
          %a{:href => 'https://docs.google.com/document/d/1_bZ2_KQGbomwdmbYg3NeDhf8FLZFf7ldwCvnRhmxXtU/edit?usp=sharing'} Click here for a list of items
          that you can donate (feel free to bring just a few items or the full list)
          %strong by 10 December.
      .col-md-6
        %h2 karis kids christmas celebration
        %img{:src => '/images/kariskids.png'}
        %p
          This December is a highlight in the lives of the Karis Kids families in Kampala.  It is a time of coming together as a big Karis family, having fun and celebrating Christmas. All the orphan kids and their carers and staff are invited, over 600 in all!  Please consider helping to make this party possible with a small gift -
          %a{:href => "https://www.give.net/christmasparty2017"} click here to donate.
    .row
      .col-xs-12
        %h2 support the storehouse
        -#%img{:src => "/images/givehope/compassion.jpg"}
        %p
          We continue to accept donations of good quality children’s clothes and baby equipment. These can be brought to our church foyer or office lobby.
        %p
          We also give bags of food, toiletry and household items to families and individuals in Winchester, throughout the year. If you would like to donate, please
          %a{:href => 'https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/winchester-vineyard-website-assets/uploads/fs-full-list.pdf '} click here for a list of items that we collect.
    .row
      .col-xs-12
        %p.quote
          %strong Thank you so much for helping people in your community and beyond!
%section#wv-news
  .shadow
  .container
    .row
      .col-xs-12
        .wv-caption
          %h1 christmas services
          %p
            You are very welcome to attend our Christmas events and services. There is no need to book, just come along. For more information see below:
        .row
          .col-sm-12
            .row
              - @christmas_events.each do |event|
                = haml :_event, locals: { event: event }

